trans-unit.source: Enables developers to override the rendering for only the selected sections of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> controls in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Permite aos programadores substituir a composição para apenas as secções selecionadas de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> controla num <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref> zona.

trans-unit.source: Chrome refers to the peripheral user interface (UI) elements that frame each Web Parts control or server control contained in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Chrome refere-se os elementos de interface (IU) do utilizador periféricos esse período de cada controlo de peças Web ou controlo de servidor contido numa zona.

trans-unit.source: The chrome for a control includes its border, its title bar, and the icons, title text, and verbs menu that appear within the title bar.
trans-unit.target: O chrome para um controlo inclui o respetivo limite, respectiva barra de título e o ícones, o texto do título e o menu de verbos que aparecem na barra de título.

trans-unit.source: The appearance of the chrome is set at the zone level, and applies to all the controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: O aspecto do Cromado é definido ao nível da zona e aplica-se a todos os controlos na zona.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control set uses the CatalogPartChrome class to render the chrome for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: O conjunto de controlo de peças Web utiliza a classe de CatalogPartChrome para compor o chrome para <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, this class provides a way for developers to customize the rendering of any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Além disso, esta classe fornece uma forma para programadores personalizar a composição de qualquer <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controla num <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>zona.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.CreateCatalogPartChromeStyle%2A> method to customize some specific style attributes applied to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, pode substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.CreateCatalogPartChromeStyle%2A>método para personalizar a alguns atributos específicos de estilo aplicado à <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>zona.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.CreateCatalogPartChromeStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The CatalogPartChrome class contains several important methods that are useful when you want to override the rendering of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: A classe de CatalogPartChrome contém vários métodos importantes que são úteis quando pretender substituir a composição de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: One is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.%23ctor%2A> constructor, which you use when you override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A> method in a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> zone to create an instance of your custom CatalogPartChrome object.
trans-unit.target: Um é o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.%23ctor%2A>construtor, o que utilizar quando poderá substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A>método personalizadas <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase>zona para criar uma instância do seu objeto CatalogPartChrome personalizado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase.CreateCatalogPartChrome%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Another useful method is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A> method, which you can use to control the rendering of the content area of controls in a zone (as opposed to chrome elements such as headers, footers, and title bars).
trans-unit.target: Outro método útil é a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A>método, o que pode utilizar para controlar a composição da área do conteúdo de controlos numa zona (por oposição a elementos chrome, tais como cabeçalhos, rodapés de página e barras de título).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, if you want complete programmatic control over all aspects of rendering the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderCatalogPart%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Por fim, se pretender que o controlo total de programático através de todos os aspetos da composição do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos, pode substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderCatalogPart%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome.RenderCatalogPart%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome"> </xref> classe.
